## 8. Appendix

### Glossary

| Term | Definition |
| --- | --- |
| ReAct Loop | A pattern where the AI model reasons, calls a tool, observes the result, and continues reasoning until task completion |
| tool\_use\_id | A unique identifier assigned to each tool invocation by the API, used to correlate tool calls with their results |
| Continuation Request | A follow-up request sent after tool execution that includes the tool result, allowing the model to continue |
| kiro-ts | The Node.js/TypeScript backend service that mediates between the VS Code extension and the Kiro Q API |
| Anthropic Converter | A module in kiro-ts that converts between Kiro Q message format and Anthropic message format |
| Orphan tool\_result | A tool result that cannot be matched to any tool\_use in conversation history |

